name: Stanfy Open Source
tagline: Open source libraries being developed at Stanfy
body:
Stanfy Open Source
==================
We use open source to build our own products and provide services. And here are some projects we develop internally and release for community.
https://github.com/stanfy

[gson-xml](http://github.com/stanfy/gson-xml)
--------
Java library for XML deserialization.

[DyCI](http://github.com/dyci)
----
Dynamic code injection for iOS projects - powerful tool that accelerates apps development in Xcode and AppCode environments.

[enroscar](http://github.com/stanfy/enroscar)
--------
A set of libraries we actively use to develop for Android platform.

[mattock](http://github.com/stanfy/mattock)
-------
JUni4 tests runner for Android.

[gae-go-testing](http://github.com/stanfy/gae-go-testing)
--------------
Go lang package for writing tests for AppEngine platform.
